ExecDesc.value: Apple QuickTime SMIL File Handling Integer Overflow

EngDesc.value: An integer overflow vulnerability exists in Apple QuickTime. The vulnerability is due to the way QuickTime parses specially crafted SMIL documents. A remote attacker could exploit this vulnerability by persuading a user to open a specially crafted SMIL file or access a malicious web page, potentially causing arbitrary code to be injected and executed in the security context of the logged in user.
